OL,3,CAbortion buffer zone legislation not
OL,4,Cenforceable when clinics closed,
OL,5,Cpolice say
OL,7,FAbortion buffer zones cannot be
OL,8,Fenforced when clinics are closed,
OL,9,Fpolice have said in an email seen by
OL,10,Fthe PA news agency.
OL,12,FThe legislation ` which started as a
OL,13,Fmember's Bill proposed by Green MSP
OL,14,FGillian Mackay ` enforced 200-metre
OL,15,Fexclusion zones around 30 sites in
OL,16,FScotland in an attempt to limit
OL,17,Fprotests held outside of clinics.
