OL,7,FBut in an email between a police
OL,8,Finspector in Glasgow and an MSP `
OL,9,Fpassed to PA by a third party ` the
OL,10,Fofficer says legal advice from Police
OL,11,FScotland lawyers and the Crown Office
OL,12,Fconcluded the legislation cannot be
OL,13,Fenforced when clinics are not
OL,14,Foperating.
