OL,7,FThe exchange was sparked after the MSP
OL,8,Fsought clarity about a protest held
OL,9,Foutside the Sandyford Clinic in
OL,10,FGlasgow by the Scottish Family Party
OL,11,Fon April 12, which was closed due to
OL,12,Fit being a Saturday, telling police
OL,13,Fconstituents had been "understandably
OL,14,Fdistressed" by the protest.
