OL,3,CAbortion buffer zone legislation not
OL,4,Cenforceable when clinics closed,
OL,5,Cpolice say
OL,7,F"The advice given from a Police
OL,8,FScotland Senior Solicitor (who also
OL,9,Fconsulted with colleagues), and a
OL,10,FPrincipal PF (procurator fiscal)
OL,11,FDepute was that if the premises are
OL,12,Fclosed then the threshold for a breach
OL,13,Fof the legislation was not met," the
OL,14,Femail said.
OL,16,F"The PF also advised they would not
OL,17,Fprosecute any breach of legislation
OL,18,Fwhen the premises were closed.
