OL,3,CAbortion buffer zone legislation not
OL,4,Cenforceable when clinics closed,
OL,5,Cpolice say
OL,7,F"This is based on when the protected
OL,8,Fpremises are closed and if there is no
OL,9,Fprospect of service users/ providers
OL,10,Fbeing influenced/alarmed and/or
OL,11,Fharassed/prevented from accessing
OL,12,Fservices by any protesters' action,
OL,13,Fthen enforcement would have no lawful
OL,14,Fbasis.
OL,16,F"I fully suspect that The Scottish
OL,17,FFamily Party has also taken legal
OL,18,Fadvice themselves and been advised in
OL,19,Fa similar fashion to above, hence
OL,20,Ftheir choice to hold the event on a
OL,21,FSaturday."
