OL,7,FResponding to the email, Ms Mackay
OL,8,Fsaid she would be seeking a meeting
OL,9,Fwith Police Scotland and the Scottish
OL,10,FGovernment on the issue.
OL,12,F"This is a very surprising and
OL,13,Fdisappointing intervention from Police
OL,14,FScotland," she said.
OL,16,F"The intention of my Act has always
OL,17,Fbeen for buffer zones to apply all
OL,18,Fday, every day, like most laws. This
OL,19,Fwas made very clear during the passing
OL,20,Fof the Act.
