OL,3,CAbortion buffer zone legislation not
OL,4,Cenforceable when clinics closed,
OL,5,Cpolice say
OL,7,F"The committee scrutinising the Act
OL,8,Fdiscussed proposals that would have
OL,9,Flimited the operating hours of buffer
OL,10,Fzones but did not support them and
OL,11,Fthey were not moved or included in the
OL,12,Flegislation.
OL,14,F"I will be writing to Police Scotland
OL,15,Fand will seek an urgent meeting with
OL,16,Fthem and the Scottish Government to
OL,17,Fensure that the law is being enforced
OL,18,Fand that there are consequences for
OL,19,Fpeople who breach it.
