OL,7,F"Abortion rights are human rights, and
OL,8,Fboth patients and staff should be able
OL,9,Fto access healthcare without having to
OL,10,Fpass protesters and banners."
OL,12,FA spokeswoman for the Scottish
OL,13,FGovernment said: "Safe access zones
OL,14,Fare designed to safeguard a woman's
OL,15,Fright to access healthcare and to
OL,16,Fdignity and respect when they need it
OL,17,Fmost.
